Why This Project Matters

Many enterprise environments rely on centralized platforms to monitor infrastructure health, endpoint status, service availability, and network conditions. Without proper observability, administrators may struggle to quickly identify the cause of infrastructure issues or endpoint failures.

This project demonstrates how a small enterprise-style lab can use:

Active Directory
DNS
Domain-joined endpoints
Zabbix-based monitoring

to improve visibility, support troubleshooting, and lay the foundation for scalable infrastructure monitoring.

